author: crossley
msg: Separate message body from logile.
Don't use "--" as the separator. Email client think that it is a signature.

author: dlydick
msg: Add boolean to mark when the JVM has been completely initialized.
Remove class_load_from_prchar() for everything after java.lang.Object
and the Java primatives in favor of a simple class_load_resolve_clinit()
and move loading of java.lang.Thread to be with the others instead of
after secondary startup classes.
Substitute portable_XXX() version of system calls and library calls.
Updated ARCH_xxx() macros for better diagnostic support.
Minor documentation adjustments.
